CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 9, 1959, pg. A16, reads: "Sharp Pair - Robert Dunn and Catherine Bettis of Philadelphia were striking as they walked out together during the Beauty Shop Owners' show, which is an annual event during their beauty week celebration."
TitMainTitle: Robert Dunn and Catherine Bettis wearing hats at Beauty Shop Owners' fashion show, Roosevelt Hotel
